CM_ SG_ 1374 perf_mod_st "Performance mode state, either Pending (_PND) or Confirmed (_CFMD).
Pending state is either triggered when driver presses one of the perf_mod_swt_req buttons or when GVCU sends the actual Performance mode as Pending, and corresponds to a blinking button on HU.
Confirmed state is triggered only by GVCU actual Performance Mode state, and corresponds to a fixed button.";
